EN: We hope to distribute resources evenly.

ZH: 他们的家庭情况都很艰苦，均需要帮助。
EN: Their family situations are all very difficult, and they all need help.

ZH: 她一直以来对每个人都很均等。
EN: She has always been fair to everyone.

ZH: 今年的收入均比去年高。
EN: This year's income is higher than last year's on average.

ZH: 这两座山的高度均为2000米。
EN: The heights of these two mountains are both 2000 meters.

ZH: 这个盘子里的水果均是新鲜的。
EN: The fruits in this plate are all fresh.

ZH: 他坚持认为大家都应该均分。
EN: He insists that everyone should share equally.

ZH: 这份工作的风险均由我们承担。
EN: The risks of this job are borne by us.

ZH: 他们的成绩均比以前有了明显的进步。
EN: Their grades have all shown significant improvement compared to before.

ZH: 这家餐厅的菜品质量均有保证。
EN: The quality of the dishes in this restaurant is guaranteed.

ZH: 我们要确保每个人都得到均等的机会。
EN: We must ensure that everyone gets equal opportunities.

ZH: 这个小组的成员均来自不同的国家。
EN: The members of this group come from different countries.

ZH: 这些学生的观点均值得尊重。
EN: The views of these students are all worthy of respect.

ZH: 所有选手的起跑线均要对齐。
EN: The starting lines of all participants must align.

ZH: 我们要求每个人的言行均谨慎。
EN: We require everyone to be cautious in their words and actions.

ZH: 这些书籍的价值均超过我们的预期。
EN: The value of these books exceeds our expectations.

